OL,3,CMan charged after 39kg of cocaine
OL,4,Cseized
OL,6,FA man has been charged after 39kg of
OL,7,Fcocaine was seized from his vehicle,
OL,8,Fin what police are describing as 'one
OL,9,Fof the most significant drug seizures'
OL,10,Fin Cumbria.
OL,12,FCourtney Gaston-Hird, 34, of Sandholme
OL,13,FLane, Lincoln, was charged following a
OL,14,Fpolice vehicle stop near Penrith on
OL,15,FWednesday (3 June). The 34-year-old
OL,16,Fwas arrested following a short on-foot
OL,17,Fpursuit and officers then carried out
OL,18,Fa search of this vehicle.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
