OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1780830169
OL,3,CMan charged after 39kg of cocaine
OL,4,Cseized
OL,6,FPolice say they found 39 'blocks' of
OL,7,Fcocaine, with an estimated street
OL,8,Fvalue of nearly #4 million.
OL,10,FHe has been charged with possession
OL,11,Fwith intent to supply a Class A drug.
OL,13,FHe appeared before Barrow Magistrates
OL,14,FCourt today on Friday 5 June.
OL,16,FThe seizure was part of Operation
OL,17,FAlliance, which is Cumbria Police's
OL,18,Fresponse to protect the county against
OL,19,Fserious and organised crime.
